      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LEICA PHOENIX (1) turned in a better effort at Hobart last start, finishing third behind Silent Elsie (26.56) in a Special conditions race. Expected to feature in the finish again. BUCKLE UP ALURA (2) could manage only fifth after copping a check in the run last time in a Grade 6 at this track, finishing 7 lengths from the winner (30.64). Gets chance to atone. ZIPPING EMILY (3) steps out for the first time at this track. Missed the frame last time when 4th and beaten 9 lengths (30.59) at The Gardens. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Warrants plenty of respect. CHEERLEADER (4) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.",
